Hello! Here it is, the first RP map for CS:S for FPSBanana for you people of the community to get your hands on.
Before I get down to explainging this, I owe great credit to Natalya - Creator of RP Mod (CS:S) - http://www.lady-natalya.info/index.php - Also credit to f.kalkman - Orgins of map.
But yeah.. All original content to him.
This great map contains the following and more,
-Petrol station
-Park/Playground.
-Flasts, multiple rooms - Lockable.
-Custom materials & models.. Everywhere.
-Cafe/Restaraunt.
-Cinema. - Working.
-Gym/Workout.
-Gunshop. - Realistic, to a exstent.
-Police station W/Riotsheilds.
Disarming jail cells.

-Toilates
-Tools shop.
-Tech shop/Computing.
-Mayors office, requires code.
-Hospital.
-Overall, all features of a small street.

Took about a month to complete. With help from multiple others.. As listed in credit section.
Very important if your going to use this, it also could be used for a DM Map, would be fun..
You must add this to your server.cfg.. 
"net_maxfilesize 25"
The defult is not large enough. #30 would be a good value to put it at.
There may be a video coming soon, if anyone can make one feel free to.
Works very well, no known bugs.. 
Skybox may be slightly glitchie but that depends on your PC/hardware.
I belive that is all. 
Hope you enjoy this map and have fun.

A small jump map that is rather hard in some places. Yes, thats right, I did not add CT spawns, because of killing. Roxjump is no kill flat out jump. The other jump maps may have killing, I don't know, because I've never downloaded one. I couldn't simply do game_player_equip because of the slower moving, which causes impossible jumps in this map including: The first and second jumps. The end is a idle antlionguard, and if you touch the THE END! sign you are teleported back to start. Yes, I'm aware of the small amounts of fall damage you take when you get teleported back there. I'm not fixing this because honestly I haven't even made it through the whole thing twice, thats how hard and challanging this map is. It may seem short, but I thought it was fun when I tested it, so I posted it here on FPSB. I am also aware of the raft moving slow. I was not careful on the construction on this raft and forgot to set the speed. Now it moves at 50 or 100 speed, which is pretty slow. Sometimes the raft goes faster than normal, could be a bug, because I compiled in Fast Mode, but its a good bug because sometimes you dont want to wait longer to get there. Though im shocked with the speed of the raft. I found it realistic because you can only paddle a raft so fast. But, no one likes waiting do they? To start the raft, look down on the middle of it and press USE(E key). Have fun! I added sound effects for when you spawn and when you fall into the lava. None of these sounds are custom. Also, by the screenshots you may be able to tell this is not mat_fullbright.

Attention : this isn’t a deathrun map but it may be for those servers because it has some similarities with it. Read the continuation to have some explanations.

Name of map : r2s_ghn_peril (r2s means “run to survive”, ghn is our initials).
This map is for deathrun servers for the moment, if in the future other r2s maps are created and r2s servers get born, then we’ll change of section naturely. 

The difference with deathrun is that there aren’t any button, the traps are on the map and don’t kill, they just slow down the runners.

There are 33 CT max and 33 T max. The noblock permit to everyone to start at the same line, there are 10 seconds before the beginning at every round. People have to run faster than all their team, passing the obstacles faster than all their mates. There are some checkpoints, when a checkpoint alarm is ringing and lighted in red, that means that the quota of players is almost reached. When it’s reached, all the players who are behind the checkpoint place die. After the last checkpoint, only 5 people still be alive. Always one player of each team gotta pass a checkpoint nevertheless. At the end, there is a knife room arena, since one player has the knife, all his team is dying except himself. The two survivors have 30 seconds to kill the opponent, with some music (2 from each creator, so there are 6 musics).

Thank you to all the beta testers and to all the servers who’ll accept to implant this map on their deathrun servers or fun servers if they think it’s too much different.
If someone wants to create another r2s map, he’s welcome to use this prefix.
